1. **Write two to three sentences on why Django is so popular among web developers.**

Django is popular among web developers because it offers **secure deployment, scalability, effective** **and fast development** with built-in features (**“batteries-included” philosophy**) such as authentication and a user-friendly admin panel. Its **Model-View-Template (MVT)** architecture simplifies database management. Additionally, Django has a large community that provides great support and resources.
